wiki.summary: “Dead” is the 8th track from VULTURES 2 featuring Future and Lil Durk. The track was first previewed during the Las Vegas Vultures Rave on December 15, 2023, and features Atlanta rapper and longtime Ye collaborator Future as well as Chicago rapper Lil Durk. An updated version of the song was previewed on Aus Taylor’s Instagram Story on February 20, 2024, this time with alternate Ty Dolla $ign lyrics. The song was previewed once again on March 9, 2024 at a friends and family listening party in Los Angeles for VULTURES 2. Read more on Last.fm.
